Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:39.11,Main,Nob,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving me such \Na wonderful name, Isaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:43.86,Main,HB1,0000,0000,0000,,Her police came back, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:45.40,Main,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,We're off.
