Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:55.37,Side Bar Bottom Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,where will it lead them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:24:00.75,Side Bar Top Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, the Farewell Shinsengumi Arc
